{"tid":802661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（文長）請絲打巴打俾建議","createTime":"2018-09-01T15:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T01:26:38.000Z","uid":171316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d56d2d49dfe7f3d699f4d942f5bfd795962770","tid":802661,"uid":171316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"小弟請各位幫幫手俾意見!<br />\n<br />\n小弟無咩拍拖經驗&hellip;係中學拍拖到大2同個女仔分左手&hellip;之後就無再拍拖了!（好大原因係我仲好鐘意個女仔，令我覺得其他女仔俾唔上佢）<br />\n<br />\n如是這過左5，6年，努力工作!個女仔都就快結婚&hellip;加上身邊人愈來愈多人都同我講年紀都唔細要拍拖，結婚。差不多要向人生另一階段發展!我就開始玩交友apps!（工作環境多人妻和年紀大ee，唔可以係工作環境認識）<br />\n<br />\n7月左右同一個女仔幾岩傾，第一次約出黎去睇戲食飯。我覺得個女仔性格隨和，相處好舒服，興趣接近。之後都keep住有WhatsApp，差不多一星期見一次，一齊食晚飯。<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎la!小弟出黎做野真係無去識女仔，無咩經驗&hellip;我應該點樣令到關係升華?表唔表白好&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心求教!"},{"pid":"92d88e7e0c6167bc580af30877f8c9f316a84b68","tid":802661,"uid":25273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"多啲肢體接觸<br />\n問題係覺得人哋對你有冇興趣先"},{"pid":"60a88bbb2cc766a745b423356349fbd841638b8e","tid":802661,"uid":171316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92d88e7e0c6167bc580af30877f8c9f316a84b68","tid":802661,"uid":25273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"多啲肢體接觸<br />\n問題係覺得人哋對你有冇興趣先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:33:44.000Z","msg":"我試過行得好近，掂到佢幾次!佢都無彈開同厭惡!<br />\n佢每次出完街，都話好開心&hellip;我都唔知真定假&hellip;"},{"pid":"9d5de58d3656cf07a808af89dc607bd605a4edd1","tid":802661,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"摸佢patpat"},{"pid":"2258bed80c2a5965cb7850c2d9c99b62b6fae116","tid":802661,"uid":25273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"約下做其他嘢囉<br />\n食飯好難有咩攻勢"},{"pid":"afb177504fb3fda290ea738dab5ad80eec1df085","tid":802661,"uid":171316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d5de58d3656cf07a808af89dc607bd605a4edd1","tid":802661,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"摸佢patpat"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"癡漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後上差館&hellip;"},{"pid":"13677d86bf5d6ab2c4de1ce54cfd58146074cfe4","tid":802661,"uid":171316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2258bed80c2a5965cb7850c2d9c99b62b6fae116","tid":802661,"uid":25273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"約下做其他嘢囉<br />\n食飯好難有咩攻勢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"有無好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab2a860c379bc38da59567f94433ee903a49a1c","tid":802661,"uid":171316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"希望大家幫手!"}]}